            "is_prior_year_field": false,
            "draft_value": null,
            "rationale": "The request type is programmatic, not language-based. This section does not apply.",
            "confidence": "low"
          },
          {
            "field_id": "google_forms:01:entry_375340318:9728ca8ef92c",
            "label": "Explanation/Rationale for Request",
            "help_text": null,
            "field_type": "textarea",
            "required": true,
            "options": null,
            "is_constituent_info": false,
            "is_prior_year_field": false,
            "draft_value": "* Sustains the U.S. strategic edge in space science, ensuring American norms for exploration prevail over international competitors.\n* Requests a 24% increase over FY 2026 enacted levels to recover from prior shortfalls and ensure project continuity.\n* Strengthens the STEM talent pipeline by supporting university-led research and local high-tech employment.\n* Guarantees that the nation's most ambitious scientific questions are answered through the rigorous, nonpartisan Decadal Survey process.",
